name: Atama o Kitaete Asobu Taisen Yajirushi Puzzle: Puppynu Vector One
overview: Atama o Kitaete Asobu Taisen Yajirushi Puzzle: Puppynu Vector One is a stacking puzzle game. The board is full of arrows and you try to throw your arrows to create as long combo chains as possible while your opponent is doing the same.
